Maaii, the app for free talk and text: now available on Android



七月 9th, 2012
 | Categories: Focus



Mobile voice &  text platform now delivers free app-to-app calls, text messages,
facebook  phone calls, and international voice roaming 
Maaii, a  new multi-platform mobile application that allows users to make calls and send  text messages to contacts and social network friends for free, announces the  launch of its beta on Google Play.
In the six months since Maaii’s iOS  launch, the mobile app has attracted more than 1 million registered users.  With  the release of its Android beta version, Maaii is set to deliver the same rich  HD quality voice communications and innovative Facebook integration to even more  devices worldwide, for free.
『Our inclusion in Google Play  demonstrates Maaii’s commitment to delivering extraordinary value to our growing  user base. The successful launch of our iOS app resulted in a cascade of  requests for access to our Android app and we’ve responded by opening up our  beta testing to the public. The results thus far have been staggering, with tens  of thousands of testers already participating,” said Chris Lewis, Vice President  for Maaii.
“Android users can now enjoy a mobile  VoIP application which connects them to their social networks on their  smartphones for free. We’re excited to add that this is only the beginning. We  aim to expand the service to include a wide range of integrated voice and  messaging services that will change the way people communicate,” Lewis  continued.
Maaii for Android features all of the  key functions the iOS version provides including:

·          Predictive Dialing, to help  users quickly find contacts as they dial a number.
·          Social Sync, which allows users  to place phone calls or send texts to Facebook friends, even without knowing  their phone number.
·          Push Notifications, which alert  users of incoming calls, messages and friends joining Maaii.
·          International Voice Roaming,  which allows users to make calls to landline and mobile numbers of friends who  don’t yet have Maaii in more than 200 destinations  Worldwide.

In addition to Android beta, Maaii  recently launched a developer SDK allowing 3rd party developers to add HD voice  communications into their native iOS or Android applications. This is backed by  its extensive operator network and is the precursor to a range of SDK services  that will form a suite of enriched platform services.
About Maaii  Limited
Maaii is a free mobile communications app for iOS and  Android devices that combines voice calls, instant messaging and social network  integration. Maaii users can register with their mobile number and make free  calls to other Maaii users, or call mobile and landline numbers worldwide with  MaaiiOut™. Maaii focuses on three areas of business: iOS and Android  applications marketed to consumers worldwide; hosted and co-branded applications  offered from the cloud as a platform-as-a-service (PaaS) and an open platform  that empowers third party developers to build HD voice-enabled applications that  run on the proprietary, global Maaii network. For more information, visit:  http://www.maaii.com.
 


